title: (x) Visitnortheastengland.com handwriting? - probably handwritten {Paul S, Jan}
content:
Does anyone know what font this is? I've seen this one in a brochure and they had some more text in this _font_.

Look at the two ‘Passionate’. Each and every letter is different.  
Handwritten.
